Package it.polimi.se2019.controller

Class RequestDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.rmi.server.RemoteObject
      • java.rmi.server.RemoteServer
        • java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
          • it.polimi.se2019.controller.RequestDispatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RequestDispatcherInterface, java.io.Serializable, java.rmi.Remote
    public class RequestDispatcher
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements RequestDispatcherInterface
    Dispatcher class used by the VirtualView to allow the use of a EventHandler for each Receiving type; if null, the type can't be accepted. Locking on an object for fixing lack of RMI documentation on synchronization.
    See Also:
